caption.p: Dissemination of CHIKV in Ae. aegypti from Madeira Island. Mosquitoes were sacrificed, and heads were removed for viral titration at days 3, 6, 9 and 14 after infection on C6/36 cells. The numbers of analysed mosquitoes are given in parentheses. An asterisk refers to significant difference ( P-value < 0.05). Error bars refer to the standard deviation
